CALL for Participation to AXMEDIS2007
3rd International Conference on Automated Production of Cross Media Content 
for Multi-channel Distribution

Scientific papers accepted so far, programme include:
http://axmedis2007.upf.edu/index.php?id=12

Workshops include:
- 3rd i-Maestro Workshop on Technology Enhanced Music Education (call is still open)
- Technologies for Content Enrichment in the Web2.0 era, VARIAZIONI project

Panels include:
- Digital context, collective licensing and cultural diversity; the way forward
- Architectures for security and DRM, VISNET-II
- Rights Expression Languages Interoperability

Tutorials include:
- Content production and distribution for multichannel distribution
- AXMEDIS automated content production and processing
- etc.

The registration page is open with early registration rate is
http://axmedis2007.upf.edu/index.php?id=5

